Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:20.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}My life I trade it for your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:24.88,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}头也不回就展翅高翔
