Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在塔利比亚回归联合之际  美国总统进行了紧急访问
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,订立了物资援助和增加能量供给的协约
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  一连串的事件全都是美国和塔利比亚策划好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在此事件中Celestial Being被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being不过是贯彻了根除战争的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而对塔利比亚展开了攻击而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是受到世人的憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要利用他们什么的还得重新考虑才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜公主  差不多该去各国周游了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待着您的好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽力而为的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了挽救阿扎提斯坦  太阳光能量是必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:01:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我问一句  您为何接受了这个使命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问么  当然是因为只有我才能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:44.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}#05  脱离极限的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:46.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的天柱交通班车E603…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:51.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}人革联  轨道电梯  线性列车等候大厅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  你也没必要特地来送我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好这边的分公司有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  沙慈  一定要好好学哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是低费用的见习旅行  这旅行费也是我付的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  给你造成了压力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝硬是要单独房间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  有钱的大小姐真是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路…路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好照顾沙慈的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝在我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  别因为是旅行而太放纵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对路易丝乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈不会有这种歪脑筋的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  我觉得这女孩不太适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都听到了哦  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手续办妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的…性能测试…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐已把任务计划发过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是监视MS的性能测试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据情况  也可实施摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得小心点  阿里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自塔利比亚事件以来  我们被全世界都讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎各位今天搭乘天柱交通公司班车E603
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本线性列车是到低轨道平台——真柱的特快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达时间是18点32分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格林威治标准时间为明天3点32分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初期加速已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起  本列车将开始缓慢的减速
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车厢内将构成无重力状态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在松开保险带时千万注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳光发电装置建设计划
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是人类在地球的化石原料枯竭后\N为了获得新的能源  而于半个世纪前展开的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发电装置以全长近5万公里的轨道电梯为中心…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  我还没问过少尉你为何要志愿加入超人机关呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是志愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为超兵计划而培养出的Design Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超兵1号由置于体内的纳米机器来保持身体机能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可在宇宙环境中进行长时间活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外  通过增强各神经系统的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必说明了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有什么地方不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机关对自己的所为不觉得什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了在恶劣的宇宙环境中压制敌人  少尉的存在不可或缺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,储藏太阳光能量的卫星通过微波通信而向轨道电梯提供电能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后通过电梯而向地面上的各地区输送电流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天的电流供给量为1.2能量单位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:07:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前  参加人类革新联盟的35个国家由能源中部直接供给电源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝  我还在看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  去玩吧  去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:19.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}人革联  低轨道平台  真柱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了啦  被你拉着到处转
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你耐力好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沙慈·克洛斯罗德和路易丝·哈莱维吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是负责你们见习的摩尔斯·阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到低轨道平台——真柱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  你知道为什么需要低轨道环吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  使磁性流体在环内流动以产生向心力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而使整个平台稳定在轨道高度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  沙慈  快来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样  路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能随便去那种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与看影像时完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽是1万千米的高度  但还有一定的重力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是跨出一步  那就会掉向地球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈真笨  好好救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这边  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  与超兵1号的反应速度相适应的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MSJ-06II-SP  铁人  桃子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁人桃子  我的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对付Gundam的王牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用完餐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否要什么饮料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢从高处看地球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能体会你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面上太让人烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还出现了Celestial Being什么的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要达了  在那之前请好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:18.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}人革联  低轨道平台  重力区
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有重力真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  马上到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了考察机体的运动性能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尝试以最大加速度沿确定的轨道环绕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达到最大加速
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最大加速度下只和路径偏差了0.25
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是超兵的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  她还只是个少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉  偏离规定轨道了  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中…中校  有什么东西在刺激我的头…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这头疼是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死  是哪里来的什么家伙  随便进入老子身体中的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停不下来吗  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了行星碎片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁  那个家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是重力块吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出事故了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我不想死！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我吧  阿里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉…少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理中心  我是谢尔盖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我重力块的受损情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  根据事故发生时的紧急联络判断
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被分离开的第7重力区域里有232名乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援队呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计在7分钟后派出救援队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也已经向负责守备的小分队发出紧急出发的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由于爆炸所产生的冲击以及空气的泄露
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7重力区域的速度急速下降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14分钟后将会落入地球引力圈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入救援行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让回收少尉机体的部队出动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  质量那么大的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人命关天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援队出发了啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在时间上怎么也赶不上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力块会被地球的引力牵引
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:14:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  阿里路亚·哈普提兹姆他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个重力块完全脱离了空间站
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说在漂流中？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援队马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持到那时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有7分钟就要到达临界脱离区域了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让重力块回到原本的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有让那个庞然大物加速才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才计算了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个重力区域还有5分钟就要落入地球引力圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙…沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑吧  只剩下5分钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7区域的质量太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠这台机体的推进力…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离到达临界脱离区域还有200秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去我的机体也要被吸入重力圈里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能对这200多人见死不救吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙啊  你为什么如此无情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个以高速接近的机体是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么到现在雷达才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亚  阿里路亚·哈普提兹姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你的任务呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是无法明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙漂流者的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离到达临界脱离区域还有20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:16:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又  又有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  Celestial Being竟然会救人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就看皇小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美发出了紧急机密讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救人…  那个孩子在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速报  空间站事故的失踪者名单出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有Gundam那样的推进力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持现状也已经是极限了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  燃料用尽以后  也只能落入地球圈了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得到吗  全员集中到中央区域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音  是Gundam的机师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍  不想死的话  赶快集中到中央去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…援救行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻男子的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定这次就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想现在就对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到吗  Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个东西马上就要进入脱离极限的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了  赶快放开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being是不允许失败的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对沙慈你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Meister可不是一个人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子高浓度压缩中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距填充完毕还有20  19  18  17  16…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射方向的轴线上有云挡着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它切开  刹那！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填充完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒的支援  皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从地面狙击那两个重力块让它们分离开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减轻重量后  再把它推入安全轨道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援队来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中…中校  Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援行动是最优先的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是我  也是知道感恩的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速报  全员安全获救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吠陀安排的任务  优先去救人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  Dynames的高精度狙击能力也向全世界暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要大幅度修正本来的计划呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变原来的任务  向洛克恩·斯托拉托斯下达命令的可是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是为了帮助阿里路亚·哈普提兹姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为了保护Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是只要适性相符合  就都能乘上Gundam的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们差点就死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最后想说的…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在一成不变的战场上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.09,0:23:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being也不会保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.04,0:23:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配置了新武器的Gundam们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要向世界表明自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「七剑」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经再也回不来了


